   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"(Christian sign) Dorothe writing to his brother Martyre: please send me your gems (?), and I shall cut these pieces of stone in my place and send them to you quickly, when they are ready for you. But don't be concerned about sending bread, for we have barley. Pray for me."</ab>
         </div>
